videos.description: UConn guard Alterique Gilbert feeds a bounce pass to Eric Cobb, who takes a dribble and puts in a layup vs. Iowa.
videos.headline: UConn's Gilbert finds Cobb for layup

videos.description: Iowa's Nicholas Baer hustles to grab a loose ball and the Hawkeyes swing the ball around the perimeter with Luka Garza hitting a 3-pointer vs. UConn.
videos.headline: Iowa's hustle for loose ball leads to 2nd-chance points

videos.description: Iowa's Tyler Cook drives to the hoop vs. UConn and finishes for the hoop and the harm in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Iowa's Cook drives for and-1

videos.description: UConn guard Alterique Gilbert comes down with a rebound and hits Tarin Smith up ahead for a scoop layup.
videos.headline: UConn's Gilbert hits Smith in transition for nifty layup

videos.description: Iowa's Tyler Cook posts up a UConn defender, spins to the hoop and puts down a one-handed dunk in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Iowa's Cook spins and hammers down reverse dunk

videos.description: Iowa's Tyler Cook cuts through the lane and throws down a one-handed jam with authority vs. UConn.
videos.headline: Cook rises up for another powerful dunk
